* TESTZCV1.MLC                                                      *
* Use ZCVT to access and display current PGM and IPL fields         *
*********************************************************************
* 2005-04-23 DSH         Initial version                            *
* 2006-04-23 DSH RPI-286 Dump ZCVT fields starting at X'2000' after *
*                        PSA                                        *
